<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="hall-n">hall <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /hɔːl/    美 /hɔl/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>大厅；礼堂；会堂：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the Great Hall of the People 
人民大会堂</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I was saving a seat for you in the dining hall. 
我正在餐厅给你占座。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>门厅；(大厦的) 过道；走廊：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She ran into the hall and up the stairs. 
她跑进门厅，冲上楼梯。</p></div></div>